aboutUs: Gitothua Judo Club is a premier judo training center located in the heart of Central Kenya. Established in 2005, our club has been dedicated to promoting the art of judo and nurturing talent from grassroots to elite levels. With a team of experienced coaches and state-of-the-art facilities, we provide comprehensive training programs for judokas of all ages and skill levels. Our mission is to foster discipline, respect, and excellence both on and off the mat. Join us to be part of a vibrant judo community and take your skills to the next level.

Join us as we continue to build on our legacy of success.
